can be related to the rapid transformation
of the free fatty acids present into hydroperoxides. Moreover, dry-
ing + boiling (60 min) significantly increase the acidity of walnut oil.
This result is in accordance with those of Tenyang et al. (2017) who
showed that the acid value of sesame oil significantly increases during
boiling and roasting at different temperature and time.
